      <p>Designing front end,<br>hardware, and<br>everything in between.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="font-size: 30px" id="contact" class="text-center">
      <a style="color: white" href="https://www.facebook.com/anthonydresser"><i class="fa fa-facebook-square"></i></a>
